/*
    Magical whispers cause 1d8 sonic damage to attackers who hit you.
    Made the damage slightly more than the book says because we cannot
    do the +1 per level.
*/
//:://////////////////////////////////////////////
//:: Created By: Preston Watamaniuk
//:: Created On: Jan 7, 2002
